name: Solo
details:
High gain distortion pedal. Suhr Riot clone.Product Features
- All-sided high-gain distortion with excellent dynamic response and definition, especially suited for solo playing
- 3 Working Modes: Natural/Tight/Classic
- Full metal shell
- Very small and exquisite
- True bypass
- Requires DC 9V Adapter power supply
